Adedoyin is the chairman of Hilton Hotel, Ile-Ife, Osun State, the last known place that the late Adegoke lodged prior to his death. Adegoke, an MBA student of the Obafemi Awolowo University, Ile-Ife, died under suspicious circumstances at the hotel. Adegoke, who has since been buried, had arrived Ile-Ife to write his examination and lodged in the hotel before his death. Adedoyin’s son, who is also a suspect, is still at large. Details Later…